  <description><![CDATA[<p>At the foot of the pistes, this welcoming hotel, run by the Valentin family is a new addition to our programme this winter. Offering comfortable, charming accommodation in a perfect location, the hotel is ideal for families or couples. Access to and from the pistes could not be easier and the shops, restaurants and numerous bars of Les Deux Alpes are only a stroll away. Enjoy a drink in the evening in the welcoming bar or relax in the whirlpool or sauna after a day on the mountain.</p>]]></description>
